    <briefdescription>
<para>Base class for evaluating conditions determining a setting&apos;s state. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Base class for evaluating conditions determining a setting&apos;s state. The setting Data Asset has a list of VisibilityConditions, and a list of EditabilityConditions, which will be used to evaluate its specific active/disabled/hidden state. <simplesect kind="note"><para><computeroutput>Abstract</computeroutput> <computeroutput>Blueprintable</computeroutput> <computeroutput>EditInlineNew</computeroutput> <computeroutput>DefaultToInstanced</computeroutput> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
